title: Jonathan Garner: What Can SARS Tell Us About the Coronavirus?
description: On today's episode, To understand the impact of the Coronavirus on humanity, economics and markets, Chief Asia and Emerging Markets Equity Strategist Jonathan Garner draws parallels with the 2002 SARS outbreak.
